<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Frontend Development Course</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/frontend.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/Photos/smart_academy-updated.png">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <img class="logo-img" src="/Photos/smart_academy-updated.png" alt="logo" onclick="window.location.href='/home'" />
        <h2>Frontend Development</h2>
    </header>

    <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/home">Home</a>
        <a href="/courses">Courses</a>
        <a href="/aboutUs">About Us</a>
        <a href="/contactUs">Contact</a>
        <%- include('partials/cart') %>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-auth">
        <a href="/signlog" class="auth-btn">Sign Up</a>
        <button id="logoutBtn" style="display: none;">Logout</button>
    </div>

</nav>

    <div id="cartModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">&times;</span>
            <h2 class="modalTitle">Shopping Cart</h2>
            <div id="cartItems"></div>
            <div class="cart-total">
                <strong>Total: </strong>
                <span id="cartTotal">$0</span>
            </div>
            <button id="checkoutBtn" class="checkout-btn">
                Proceed to Checkout
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main>
        <div class="course-banner">
            <img src="/Photos/front.jpg" alt="Frontend Development Course" class="course-image">
        </div>

        <div class="course-content">
            <section class="overview">
                <h2>Course Overview</h2>
                <p>Master frontend web development with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to build modern, responsive websites.</p>
                
                <div class="course-meta">
                    <span class="rating">
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i> 4.8
                        <small>(3,456 ratings)</small>
                    </span>
                    <span class="students">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i> 42,150 students
                    </span>
                    <span class="instructor">
                        <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i> Esraa Abd EL-Aziz
                    </span>
                    <span class="language">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe"></i> English, Arabic
                    </span>
                    <span class="last-updated">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Last updated 15/3/2025
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="course-actions">
                    <button class="add-to-cart" data-course="frontend" data-price="999">
                        <i class="fas fa-cart-plus"></i>
                        Add to Cart - $999
                    </button>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="what-you-learn">
                <h2>What You'll Learn</h2>
                <ul class="checklist">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Build responsive websites using HTML5 and CSS3</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Master JavaScript and modern ES6+ features</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Implement interactive user interfaces</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Use CSS Flexbox and Grid for layouts</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Work with APIs and handle AJAX requests</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Optimize website performance</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Deploy websites to production</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Apply responsive design principles</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Debug and test web applications</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Build a professional portfolio</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="course-includes">
                <h2>This Course Includes</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-video"></i> 42 hours of video</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-file"></i> 15 coding exercises</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i> 5 real-world projects</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Downloadable resources</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i> Certificate of completion</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-infinity"></i> Full lifetime access</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="learning-outcomes">
                <h2>By The End Of This Course You Will Be Able To</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Create modern, responsive websites from scratch</li>
                    <li>Build interactive web applications using JavaScript</li>
                    <li>Implement professional UI/UX design principles</li>
                    <li>Work with modern web development tools</li>
                    <li>Deploy and maintain web applications</li>
                </ol>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/frontend.js"></script>
</body>
</html>